theorem Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_closure_of_P3
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P3 (A := A) → closure A = closure (interior (closure A)) := by
  intro hP3
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  ·
    have hInc : (A : Set X) ⊆ interior (closure A) := hP3
    have : (closure A : Set X) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) :=
      closure_mono hInc
    simpa using this
  ·
    have : (closure (interior (closure A)) : Set X) ⊆ closure A :=
      closure_mono (interior_subset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A)
    simpa using this

theorem Topology.closure_interior_subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure (interior A) ⊆ closure A := by
  simpa using (closure_mono (interior_subset : interior A ⊆ A))
